on exitFrame
  [  0] pushint16 1 ............................. <1>
  [  3] pusharglist 1 ........................... <1>
  [  5] extcall 12 .............................. <soundBusy(1)>
  [  7] jmpifz [ 16] ............................ if soundBusy(1) then
  [ 10] pushsymb 17 ............................. <#loop>
  [ 12] pusharglistnoret 1 ...................... <#loop>
  [ 14] extcall 3 ............................... go(#loop)
  [ 16] ret
end
